[SPEAKER_17] Evo, ja bih puno podrške ovoj gospođi da je Bog da snage.

559
00:48:12,559 --> 00:48:13,440
[SPEAKER_09] A meni ništa.

560
00:48:15,039 --> 00:48:15,840
[SPEAKER_17] I vama isto.

561
00:48:16,079 --> 00:48:17,519
[SPEAKER_17] E, znate što?

562
00:48:20,559 --> 00:48:22,320
[SPEAKER_17] Ja želim samo vašu molitvu.

563
00:48:22,880 --> 00:48:23,119
[SPEAKER_09] Dobro.

564
00:48:23,519 --> 00:48:24,639
[SPEAKER_09] Hoćemo to uspojiti sada?

565
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:32,639
[SPEAKER_17] Čijelo već je uspjelo, evo, toliko me je ono kad molite, ja sam, ne znam šta bih vam rekla.

566
00:48:33,039 --> 00:48:34,320
[SPEAKER_17] Kao da sam druga osoba.

567
00:48:34,559 --> 00:48:36,800
[SPEAKER_09] Evo, ja ću se pomoliti onda sad za vas, ali.

568
00:48:37,599 --> 00:48:39,360
[SPEAKER_09] ja ću vas uključiti sada u molitvu.

569
00:48:39,440 --> 00:48:40,800
[SPEAKER_09] Sad ćemo za svih početi moliti.

570
00:48:40,960 --> 00:48:41,199
[SPEAKER_09] Može?

571
00:48:42,159 --> 00:48:42,400
[SPEAKER_07] Može.

572
00:48:42,800 --> 00:48:45,199
[SPEAKER_09] Ok, da čujemo još koga pa ćemo početi za svih moliti.

573
00:48:45,360 --> 00:48:47,760
[SPEAKER_09] Evo, Bog vas blagoslovio i drago mi je da ste se javili.

574
00:48:49,199 --> 00:48:51,519
[SPEAKER_09] Hvala, nisam se smario, imamo još nekoga na liniji.

575
00:48:52,639 --> 00:48:54,480
[SPEAKER_13] Imate, imate, fajn, Flajda.

576
00:48:56,239 --> 00:48:57,119
[SPEAKER_09] Ja sam te ne čekao.

577
00:48:57,519 --> 00:48:59,679
[SPEAKER_13] Jednu mladu osobu sa puno godina.

578
00:49:01,119 --> 00:49:02,239
[SPEAKER_09] Mladu duhu, bravo.

579
00:49:03,199 --> 00:49:05,199
[SPEAKER_13] Čestitam, čestitam gospođo.

580
00:49:05,679 --> 00:49:07,199
