670
01:00:07,360 --> 01:00:08,159
[SPEAKER_04] Budi duhovan.

671
01:00:08,719 --> 01:00:09,440
[SPEAKER_09] Budi duhovic.

672
01:00:10,239 --> 01:00:15,840
